                  <msItem>
                     <note type="general">Written along the fibers; the back is also written along the fibers</note>
                     <note type="general">The letter consists of a long, complex sentence</note>
                     <note type="general">12 lines of writing by a large, inclined hand on what was probably the back of a reused papyrus; beginnings of 11 lines on the front (an account?) by a different, more elaborate hand; most of the space on the front is unwritten</note>
